ANY OTHER NOTES FOR THE GRADER:

If percentage of each possibility rounded to the nearest one percent, 
there would be some inaccuracy of the result, such as, we add every 
percentage of each possibility, the result maybe 99% instead of 100%.
On the other hand, if we use 100% to minus the other two possibilities,
the result may seems to be correct, but it isn't came out by real calculation.

